"Paste over a visually selected area without the selection being placed in the default register
xnoremap P Pgvy
"Keep the cursor in the middle while scrolling
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz
nnoremap n nzz
nnoremap N Nzz

inoremap <C-k> <Esc>
xnoremap <C-k> <Esc>

set number
set relativenumber
